@pixel-sheet v1
# Bespoke miniboss designs. Bosses are placed, never palette-swapped fodder:
# each route pack's miniboss gets its own authored silhouette.

@sprite sprite:boss-bramble-tyrant
description Oldwood miniboss: a towering thorn mass crowned with red blooms.
grid 16x16
anchor 8,16
channels X,E,e,T,R,r
palette palette:base
facing mirror-x 1
animations idle=anim:idle,walk=anim:walk-bob,hurt=anim:hit-flash
traits Transform,Sprite,Palette,Facing,Animator,DepthSorted
rows
